        "title": "Tu es à quel chapitre, toi ?",
        "description": "<p><span style=\"background-color: black; color: white;\"><span class=\"TextRun SCXW31401405 BCX9\" data...",
        "content": "<p><span style=\"background-color: black; color: white;\"><span class=\"TextRun SCXW31401405 BCX9\" data-contrast=\"auto\" lang=\"FR-CA\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_EmbeddedFont&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_MSFontService&quot;, fantasy; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-ligatures: none !important; line-height: 21.5833px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; user-select: text; white-space: pre-wrap;\" xml:lang=\"FR-CA\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW31401405 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">Honnêtement. C’est quand la dernière fois que tu as lu un livre. Pour le plaisir, là. Pas parce que tu as un examen sur le sujet dans trois minutes</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW31401405 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">. Que tu t’es assis dans un divan, et que tu as décidé : Aujourd’hui, je vais lire. La réponse est probablement, si tu n’es pas comme moi</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW31401405 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"> (comprendre : un rat de bibliothèque certifié)</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW31401405 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">, il y a très longtemps. L’arrivée des jeux vidéo et des réseaux sociaux n’ont qu’empiré la situation.</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW31401405 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"> Pourtant, il y a plein d’avantages à la lecture.</span></span><span class=\"EOP SCXW31401405 BCX9\" data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_EmbeddedFont&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_MSFontService&quot;, fantasy; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 21.5833px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; user-select: text; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p></p><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhB3qHZyRd6vcdrinqQMu_CBLHuSAizYkQI7UbXlD1ybG2ARTw_O7v4jQ7k9xANJDOdNedBMDZslMIROCM2kVRjJBs_nbbhmVj5VhRyXTy9Y4sKv1r8gUOyUUOukjem_BikcbI-S99aQPxGxSA_0RH8NZGCsEGkhQ9wmWAueEj1Ck_MCcM7alhNjHN7mg/s604/book-794978__340.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><span style=\"background-color: black; color: white;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"340\" data-original-width=\"604\" height=\"360\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhB3qHZyRd6vcdrinqQMu_CBLHuSAizYkQI7UbXlD1ybG2ARTw_O7v4jQ7k9xANJDOdNedBMDZslMIROCM2kVRjJBs_nbbhmVj5VhRyXTy9Y4sKv1r8gUOyUUOukjem_BikcbI-S99aQPxGxSA_0RH8NZGCsEGkhQ9wmWAueEj1Ck_MCcM7alhNjHN7mg/w640-h360/book-794978__340.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></span></a></div><p></p><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW92398781 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; clear: both; cursor: text; direction: ltr; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Web&quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; overflow: visible; padding: 0px; position: relative; user-select: text;\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW92398781 BCX9\" paraeid=\"{b4dd3ef4-f4e8-4dd4-84bf-ef05959e3191}{201}\" paraid=\"543616439\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; font-kerning: none; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; user-select: text; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"background-color: black; color: white;\"><span class=\"TextRun Underlined SCXW92398781 BCX9\" data-contrast=\"auto\" lang=\"FR-CA\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_EmbeddedFont&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_MSFontService&quot;, fantasy; font-size: 14pt; font-variant-ligatures: none !important; line-height: 28.0583px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration-line: underline; user-select: text;\" xml:lang=\"FR-CA\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW92398781 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">Le vocabulaire</span></span><span class=\"EOP SCXW92398781 BCX9\" data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_EmbeddedFont&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_MSFontService&quot;, fantasy; font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28.0583px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p></div><p><span style=\"color: white;\"><span class=\"EOP SCXW31401405 BCX9\" data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; background-color: black; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_EmbeddedFont&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_MSFontService&quot;, fantasy; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 21.5833px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; user-select: text; white-space: pre-wrap;\"></span></span></p><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW92398781 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; clear: both; cursor: text; direction: ltr; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Web&quot;, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; overflow: visible; padding: 0px; position: relative; user-select: text;\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW92398781 BCX9\" paraeid=\"{b4dd3ef4-f4e8-4dd4-84bf-ef05959e3191}{207}\" paraid=\"78578754\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; font-kerning: none; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; user-select: text; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"background-color: black; color: white;\"><span class=\"TextRun SCXW92398781 BCX9\" data-contrast=\"auto\" lang=\"FR-CA\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_EmbeddedFont&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_MSFontService&quot;, fantasy; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-ligatures: none !important; line-height: 21.5833px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\" xml:lang=\"FR-CA\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW92398781 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">Je ne suis pas en train de dire que </span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW92398781 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">tu vas</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW92398781 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"> devenir Shakespeare après deux pages, mais si </span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW92398781 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">tu</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW92398781 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"> lis un certain temps, </span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW92398781 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">tu vas</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW92398781 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"> progressivement absorber plus de mots </span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW92398781 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">que si tu ne lisais absolument rien. Et plus tu lis, plus c’est facile et tu dois faire de moins en moins d’allers-retours entre le dictionnaire</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW92398781 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"> (ou ton téléphone…)</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW92398781 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"> et l’endroit où tu lis. D’accord, tu utilises probablement Google, mais au</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW92398781 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">x</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW92398781 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"> rare</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW92398781 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">s</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW92398781 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"> cas où tu utilises encore la version papier, dis-toi que ça va commencer à être moins dur pour tes bras.</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW92398781 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"> Si tu ne fais que lire 20 minutes par jour, ça revient à 1,8 millions de mots par an. Penses-y un peu.</span></span><span class=\"EOP SCXW92398781 BCX9\" data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_EmbeddedFont&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_MSFontService&quot;, fantasy; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 21.5833px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW262646127 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; clear: both; cursor: text; direction: ltr; margin: 0px; overflow: visible; padding: 0px; position: relative; user-select: text;\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW262646127 BCX9\" paraeid=\"{b4dd3ef4-f4e8-4dd4-84bf-ef05959e3191}{249}\" paraid=\"1725495563\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; font-kerning: none; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; user-select: text; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"background-color: black; color: white;\"><span class=\"TextRun Underlined SCXW262646127 BCX9\" data-contrast=\"auto\" lang=\"FR-CA\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_EmbeddedFont&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_MSFontService&quot;, fantasy; font-size: 14pt; font-variant-ligatures: none !important; line-height: 28.0583px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration-line: underline; user-select: text;\" xml:lang=\"FR-CA\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW262646127 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">Le stress</span></span><span class=\"EOP SCXW262646127 BCX9\" data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_EmbeddedFont&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_MSFontService&quot;, fantasy; font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28.0583px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p></div><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW92398781 BCX9\" paraeid=\"{b4dd3ef4-f4e8-4dd4-84bf-ef05959e3191}{207}\" paraid=\"78578754\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; font-kerning: none; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; user-select: text; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: white;\"><span class=\"EOP SCXW92398781 BCX9\" data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; background-color: black; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_EmbeddedFont&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_MSFontService&quot;, fantasy; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 21.5833px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"></span></span></p><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW262646127 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; clear: both; cursor: text; direction: ltr; margin: 0px; overflow: visible; padding: 0px; position: relative; user-select: text;\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW262646127 BCX9\" paraeid=\"{b4dd3ef4-f4e8-4dd4-84bf-ef05959e3191}{255}\" paraid=\"1862774904\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; font-kerning: none; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; user-select: text; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"background-color: black; color: white;\"><span class=\"TextRun SCXW262646127 BCX9\" data-contrast=\"auto\" lang=\"FR-CA\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_EmbeddedFont&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_MSFontService&quot;, fantasy; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-ligatures: none !important; line-height: 21.5833px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\" xml:lang=\"FR-CA\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW262646127 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">Tout le monde est stressé. Des fois, c’est mérité, d’autres fois, ce serait mieux qu</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW262646127 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">e l’angoisse</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW262646127 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"> reste dans son trou. Quand ça arrive, il se peut que tu doives faire autre chose (comme finir l’examen sur ledit livre), mais sinon, tu peux essayer de lire un livre. C’est relaxant,</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW262646127 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"> en partie</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW262646127 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"> parce que à cet instant-là, tu n’es plus la personne avec le problème :</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW262646127 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"> C’est le personnage </span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW262646127 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">principal qui doit</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW262646127 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"> faire face à ses problèmes bien loin de ta réalité :</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW262646127 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"> affronter un dragon,</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW262646127 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"> grimper une montagne, ou </span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW262646127 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">combattre</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW262646127 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"> le </span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW262646127 BCX9\" data-contrast=\"auto\" lang=\"FR-CA\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_EmbeddedFont&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_MSFontService&quot;, fantasy; font-size: 11pt; font-style: italic; font-variant-ligatures: none !important; line-height: 21.5833px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\" xml:lang=\"FR-CA\">big boss</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW262646127 BCX9\" data-contrast=\"auto\" lang=\"FR-CA\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_EmbeddedFont&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_MSFontService&quot;, fantasy; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-ligatures: none !important; line-height: 21.5833px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\" xml:lang=\"FR-CA\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW262646127 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">. </span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW262646127 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">Pas toi</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW262646127 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">. Tes problèmes ne disparaitront pas comme par magie, mais tu auras la tête froide et une nouvelle perspective des choses.</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW262646127 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"> Tu trouveras peut-être même des solutions à ton problème sous forme de petit paquet cadeau imprimé.</span></span></span></p><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW215844259 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; clear: both; cursor: text; direction: ltr; margin: 0px; overflow: visible; padding: 0px; position: relative; user-select: text;\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW215844259 BCX9\" paraeid=\"{84d6ff9d-a8d8-47d7-aded-1256e060b878}{50}\" paraid=\"1826806488\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; font-kerning: none; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; user-select: text; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"background-color: black; color: white;\"><span class=\"TextRun Underlined SCXW215844259 BCX9\" data-contrast=\"auto\" lang=\"FR-CA\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_EmbeddedFont&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_MSFontService&quot;, fantasy; font-size: 14pt; font-variant-ligatures: none !important; line-height: 28.0583px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration-line: underline; user-select: text;\" xml:lang=\"FR-CA\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW215844259 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">Un peu de nouveauté</span></span><span class=\"EOP SCXW215844259 BCX9\" data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_EmbeddedFont&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_MSFontService&quot;, fantasy; font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28.0583px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p></div><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW262646127 BCX9\" paraeid=\"{b4dd3ef4-f4e8-4dd4-84bf-ef05959e3191}{255}\" paraid=\"1862774904\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; font-kerning: none; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; user-select: text; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span class=\"TextRun SCXW262646127 BCX9\" data-contrast=\"auto\" lang=\"FR-CA\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_EmbeddedFont&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_MSFontService&quot;, fantasy; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-ligatures: none !important; line-height: 21.5833px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\" xml:lang=\"FR-CA\"><span style=\"color: white;\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW262646127 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; background-color: black; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"></span></span></span></p><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW215844259 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; clear: both; cursor: text; direction: ltr; margin: 0px; overflow: visible; padding: 0px; position: relative; user-select: text;\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW215844259 BCX9\" paraeid=\"{84d6ff9d-a8d8-47d7-aded-1256e060b878}{56}\" paraid=\"986091760\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; font-kerning: none; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; user-select: text; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span class=\"TextRun SCXW215844259 BCX9\" data-contrast=\"auto\" lang=\"FR-CA\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; background-color: black; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_EmbeddedFont&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_MSFontService&quot;, fantasy; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-ligatures: none !important; line-height: 21.5833px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\" xml:lang=\"FR-CA\"><span style=\"color: white;\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW215844259 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">La lecture de permet de vivre des aventures exceptionnelles</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW215844259 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">, et de nouvelles expériences que tu voudras peut-être essayer en vrai. Je ne dis pas qu’il y a un centre de combat à dos de dragon sur Terre, mais quelque chose de plus raisonnable peut faire l’affaire. </span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW215844259 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">Ça te donner</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW215844259 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">a l’occasion de penser à des activités que tu ne connais pas, qui deviendront peut-être même tes passions! </span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW215844259 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">C’est également un bon moyen d’en apprendre plus sur d’autres cultures</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW215844259 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"> et </span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW215844259 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">d’</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW215844259 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">approfondir tes connaissances concernant certaines communautés</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW215844259 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"> peu fréquemment représentées.</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW215844259 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"> Attention de choisir le bon livre,</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW215844259 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"> puisque</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW215844259 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"> certains sont vraiment horribles, style Mein Kampf. </span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW215844259 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">Tout cela pour dire que les livres te font penser à essayer des choses que tu n’aurais même pas imaginé auparavant.</span></span></span></p><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW215844259 BCX9\" paraeid=\"{84d6ff9d-a8d8-47d7-aded-1256e060b878}{56}\" paraid=\"986091760\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; font-kerning: none; margin: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; user-select: text; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span class=\"TextRun SCXW215844259 BCX9\" data-contrast=\"auto\" lang=\"FR-CA\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_EmbeddedFont&quot;, &quot;Comic Sans MS_MSFontService&quot;, fantasy; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-ligatures: none !important; line-height: 21.5833px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\" xml:lang=\"FR-CA\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW215844259 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; background-color: black; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"><span style=\"color: white;\"><br /></span></span></span></p><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW132706504 BCX9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; clear: both; cursor: text; direction: ltr; margin: 0px; overflow: visible; padding: 0px; position: relative; user-select: text;\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW132706504 BCX9\" paraeid=\"{84d6ff9d-a8d8-47d7-aded-1256e060b878}{98}\" paraid=\"1276760566\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-user-drag: none; font-kerning: none; margin: 0px